mainTitle: ( 2 Pack ) Cheez-It Duoz Snack Crackers, Baked, Jalapeno & Cheddar Jack, 12.4 oz
keyFeatures: Light and crispy Cheddar Jack crackers and Jalapeno-flavored crackers combine for a mix of spicy, cheesy goodness in every box.
Made with 100% real cheese aged for a bold taste, these cheesy baked crackers are a classic, family-favorite snack that's perfect for kids and adults.
A travel-ready food that makes a tasty bite at home or on the go, these crackers are ideal for gatherings, parties, snack spreads, and more.
Conveniently packaged in a 2 Pack, these Jalapeno & Cheddar Jack flavored crackers can be easily stowed in lunchboxes, totes, and backpacks.
